OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772433334
OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth doodles and letter
OL,4,Cwritten when she was a girl sold for
OL,5,C#25,000
OL,7,FA handwritten letter penned by the
OL,8,Flate Queen Elizabeth II as a girl has
OL,9,Fsold for #25,000 in Kent, smashing its
OL,10,Fguide price of #2,000-#4,000.
OL,12,FThe winning bid, at Hansons
OL,13,FAuctioneers in Penshurst, followed a
OL,14,Ffierce online battle between would-be
OL,15,Fbuyers in America and the UK, before
OL,16,Fselling to a buyer from Essex.
OL,18,FJustin Matthews, from Hansons
OL,19,FAuctioneers' Penshurst said: "It was
OL,20,Fan amazing result.
OL,26,@{D@^OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
