PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772433334
OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth doodles and letter
OL,4,Cwritten when she was a girl sold for
OL,5,C#25,000
OL,7,F" When I first saw the letter, it gave
OL,8,Fme goosebumps.
OL,10,F"In 37 years in the business I had
OL,11,Fnever seen anything like it and sure
OL,12,Fenough it went on to attract worldwide
OL,13,Finterest.
OL,15,F"We had bids from all around the UK
OL,16,Fand world, including Hong Kong, but we
OL,17,Fwere delighted the determination of
OL,18,Fthe buyer meant it stayed in the UK."
