OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772433334
OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth doodles and letter
OL,4,Cwritten when she was a girl sold for
OL,5,C#25,000
OL,7,FThe one-page note, including well-
OL,8,Fdrawn doodles of dogs, horses,
OL,9,Fchildren and highwaymen, was addressed
OL,10,Fto Beatrice Stillman who in 1936
OL,11,Fbecame the head housemaid at Royal
OL,12,FLodge in Windsor.
OL,14,FIt was discovered in a suitcase two
OL,15,Fyears ago by her great nephew William
OL,16,FWestacott a farmer from Sevenoaks.
OL,18,FThe buyer from Southend, who didn't
OL,19,Fwant to be named, said he wasn't a
OL,20,Fmonarchist but bought the letter to
OL,21,Finspire his six-year-old daughter.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772433334
OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth doodles and letter
OL,4,Cwritten when she was a girl sold for
OL,5,C#25,000
OL,7,FHe said: "If I can encourage my
OL,8,Fdaughter to be as respective to
OL,9,Feveryone around her as the girl who
OL,10,Fwrote that letter then that's #25,000
OL,11,Fwell spent.
OL,13,FIt would be the best investment in her
OL,14,Feducation I can make."
OL,16,FThe letter was written by the young
OL,17,Fprincess, aged around 10, while on
OL,18,Fholiday in Praa Sands in Cornwall.
OL,20,FIn it she asks "If the birds are well,
OL,21,Fand the gold-fish haven't died."
