OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth doodles and letter
OL,4,Cwritten when she was a girl sold for
OL,5,C#25,000
OL,7,FThe letter reads:
OL,9,FSea Side, Sea Mead, Praa Sands
OL,11,FDear Beatrice,
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
