PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772433334
OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth doodles and letter
OL,4,Cwritten when she was a girl sold for
OL,5,C#25,000
OL,7,FI am sending you some primroses we
OL,8,Fpicked, wild. There are some pale pink
OL,9,Fones as well as the yellow. It is very
OL,10,Flovely here. We can go down on to the
OL,11,Fbeach from the garden. I hope the
OL,12,Fbirds are well, and the gold-fish
OL,13,Fhaven't died. Will you please give
OL,14,FCootie (Miss Coote I mean) and Mrs
OL,15,FWade some of the primroses to share.
OL,16,FJock is very well and happy here.
OL,17,FNanny and Joanna send their love to
OL,18,Fyou.
OL,20,FLove from Elizabeth.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
