OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772433334
OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth doodles and letter
OL,4,Cwritten when she was a girl sold for
OL,5,C#25,000
OL,7,FThe letter was part of a larger
OL,8,Farchive of royal memorabilia including
OL,9,FChristmas cards owned by Beatrice
OL,10,FStillman including one lot of ration
OL,11,Fbooks and signed photographs which
OL,12,Fraced past its guide price of #50-#80
OL,13,Fto sell for #3,600.
OL,15,FStillman joined the royal household in
OL,16,F1936 when Princess Elizabeth was 10
OL,17,Fand Princess Margaret, six.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
