PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772433334
OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth doodles and letter
OL,4,Cwritten when she was a girl sold for
OL,5,C#25,000
OL,7,FThe relationship was clearly a warm
OL,8,Fone, sparking a lifelong
OL,9,Fcorrespondence between the Queen
OL,10,FMother and Beatrice, who went on to
OL,11,Fmarry Alfred Twyman, a gardener at
OL,12,FWindsor Castle, in 1946.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
